  m_text: "<b>v1.1.0 (June 2026)</b>\r\n\u2022 Added player feedback collection to
    real-time database.\n\u2022 Added first-launch download/installation counter.\n\u2022
    Integrated 'Update Log & Feedback' panel into Main Menu.\r\n\r\n<b>v1.0.0 (May
    2026)</b>\r\n\u2022 Configured MediaPipe Unity Hand Tracking landmarks.\n\u2022
    Implemented player aiming and gesture-based shoot inputs.\n\u2022 Created Level
    1, Level 2, and Level 3 (Boss Fight).\r\n\r\n"
